      "content": "hey so im a designer working on a new streetwear line and i really wanna make sure it feels authentic. i dont want it to feel like cultural appropriation or like i'm just putting on a costume, u know? can u help me define what the \"authentic\" urban aesthetic actually is so i can stay true to the roots?",
